How to fix the error "permission denied"
	- Click on the project with the second button
	- Go to Android tools-->select "Fix project properties"
Other method to fix the error "permission denied"
	- chown -R user:user /bin/eclipse e.g. "chown -R alberto:alberto /bin/eclipse"
How to grant permission to Avd 
	- ~/android-sdks/platform-tools $ ./adb shell
 	- su
 	- mount -o rw,remount rootfs / 
 	- chmod 777 /mnt/sdcard 
 	- exit
 	- exit

how to change the owner of the files in a folder 
	- chown user:user folder e.g. "chown -R alberto:alberto /home/alberto/Desktop/Entornos Eclipse/Proyectos eclipse	"

